        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n(1 comment)\n\n> (1 comment)\n > \n > I have a side question about the pv-pvc change.  The size of all\n > PV's are 2Gb.  Is this a default?  I wonder if anyone investigated\n > the actual sizes of the folders being mounted to ensure we don't\n > breach size limits?  Does anyone know what happens if the data\n > grows beyond 2Gb?\n\nThis size is at this time arbitrary. Later it can be changed to better suite actual load. Or be a parameter. I think we are very far from reaching the limit though.",
